<h5>The list of documents required to register a Limited Liability Partnership are as under – </h5><br/>
<h5>For Partners (All the documents must be self-attested, scanned and uploaded)</h5>
<ul class="a">
    <li>1. PAN Card or passport (Foreign Nationals & NRIs)</li>
    <li>2. Apply for the DIN (Director Identification Number)</li>
    <li>3. Application for the name availability.</li>
    <li>4. Filing of the EMoa and EAOA to register private limited company</li>
</ul>
</div>
