<h4>For Registered Office (All documents must be scanned and uploaded)	</h4>
<ul class="a">
    <li>1. Bank Statement/ Telephone Bill/ Electricity or Gas Bill</li>
    <li>2. Notarised Rental Agreement in English</li>
    <li>3. No-Objection Certificate from the property owner</li>
    <li>4. Sale Deed/ Property Deed in English</li>
</ul>
